Ing '''Castellón''' ([[Spanish language|Espanyol]]) o '''Castelló''' ([[Valencian language|Valencian]]/[[Catalan language|Catalan]]) metung yang  [[provinces of Spain|lalawigan]] king pangulung  dake ning [[Valencia (autonomous community)|Valencian Community]], [[Espanya]]. Atin ayng sepu kareng lalawigan ning [[Valencia (lalawigan)|Valencia]], [[Teruel (lalawigan)|Teruel]], [[Tarragona (lalawigan)|Tarragona]], ampong keng  [[Mediterranean Dayat Malat]].

Ing kayang tungku iyapin ing [[Castellón de la Plana]] (ca: Castelló de la Plana). Ing lalawigan atin yang populasyun a 501,237 (2002), nung nu 30% makatuknang la king tungku, 60% king degulan a karinan apomg 85% in keng pampang.

Ing territoryu atin yang aduang amanu, keraklan magsalita lang [[Espanyol]], at dakal mu rin mangamanu lang It is a bilingual territory, with almost all inhabitants speaking Spanish, and very many also speaking the  [[Valencian dialect|Valencian]], ing labuad a opisyal a amanu.

Other major cities of the province include [[Vila-real]] (Spanish: Villarreal), [[Burriana]] and [[Vinaròs]]. There are 135 municipalities in Castellón; see [[List of municipalities in Castellón]].

